title: Introduction to Survival
description: 생존학 개론, Introduction to Survival, Introduction to the Survival Theory, The Way Of Survival ‘Remember’. ‘One, two, three, four, five, six, seven’ ‘I have to remember till the end… till the end…’ The day when my wife Julia was killed by these bastards, my whole life was filled with boiling rage. That’s right. I have to kill those bastards. “The day I get my revenge, bury me next to her.” Until then I have to survive. I bet my life on this survival game…
